[
  "Leopoldo del Pino y Calvo Sotelo inherited a stake in Ferrovial S.A., Spain's largest infrastructure construction and management company.",
  "His father, who founded the company in 1952, died in 2008. Leopoldo's two siblings also inherited stakes in Ferrovial.",
  "Leopoldo's brother Rafael del Pino is the chairman and co-CEO of Ferrovial.",
  "Leopoldo, who owns about 4% of Ferrovial, served as a board member of the company until early 2016."
